short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A WebPPL.org extension that lets the user import/export .md files or workspaces and convert datasets into variables.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds importing and exporting functions to the online editor for portability. It allows importing CSV or JSON datasets into WebPPL as well.
